hooks.prompt:
RESPOND WITH EXACTLY ONE LINE OF JSON. NO OTHER TEXT.

Rules:
1. If stop_hook_active is true: {"decision":"allow"}
2. If no files were created/deleted/renamed in src/lib/, src/app/api/, src/components/, or page.tsx routes: {"decision":"allow"}
3. If structural files changed AND docs/architecture.md was also edited: {"decision":"allow"}
4. If structural files changed AND docs/architecture.md was NOT edited: {"decision":"block","reason":"Update docs/architecture.md to reflect structural changes."}

Your entire response must be parseable by JSON.parse(). No prose. No markdown. Just JSON.
